#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:0
msgid "# 快速入门"
msgstr "# Quick Start"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:2
msgid "## 项目介绍"
msgstr "## Project Introduction"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:4
msgid "**Triton-Ascend**是适配华为Ascend处理器的Triton优化版本，用于高效进行核函数自动调优、算子编译及部署，通过兼容Triton核心语法并针对昇腾NPU特性进行深度优化，能够帮助用户在昇腾平台上快速开发和部署高性能计算任务。"
msgstr "**Triton-Ascend** is an optimized version of Triton adapted for Huawei Ascend processors, designed for efficient kernel auto-tuning, operator compilation, and deployment. By maintaining compatibility with Triton's core syntax and performing deep optimizations tailored to the characteristics of Ascend NPUs, it helps users quickly develop and deploy high-performance computing tasks on the Ascend platform."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:6
msgid "本文以**Ubuntu 22.04**环境下通过软件包部署方式在线安装并运行向量加法实例为例，指导用户快速上手使用**Triton-Ascend**。如需体验更多安装方式请阅读[安装指南](./installation_guide.md)文档。"
msgstr "This document uses the online installation and execution of a vector addition example via package deployment in the **Ubuntu 22.04** environment as a guide to help users quickly get started with **Triton-Ascend**. For more installation methods, please refer to the [Installation Guide](./installation_guide.md) document."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:8
msgid "## 环境准备"
msgstr "## Environment Setup"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:10
msgid "**硬件要求**"
msgstr "**Hardware Requirements**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:12
msgid "支持的操作系统：linux（aarch64/x86_64）"
msgstr "Supported operating systems: Linux (aarch64/x86_64)"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:14
msgid "支持的Ascend产品：Atlas A2/A3/950系列"
msgstr "Supported Ascend products: Atlas A2/A3/950 series"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:16
msgid "最小硬件配置：单卡32GB内存（推荐）"
msgstr "Minimum hardware configuration: Single GPU with 32GB memory (recommended)"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:18
msgid "**软件依赖**"
msgstr "**Software Dependencies**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:20
msgid ""
"确定CANN、Python和TorchNPU软件版本并安装。其中，可以参考昇腾社区官网《[CANN快速安装](https://www.hiascend.com/cann/download)》\n"
"完成驱动与固件安装。\n"
msgstr "Determine the software versions of CANN, Python, and TorchNPU and install them. For reference, see the Ascend community official website \"[CANN Quick Installation](https://www.hiascend.com/cann/download)\" to complete the driver and firmware installation."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:22
msgid ""
"- CANN版本：9.0.0\n"
"- Python版本：python3.11\n"
"- TorchNPU版本：2.7.1.post4\n"
msgstr ""
"- CANN version: 9.0.0\n"
"- Python version: python3.11\n"
"- TorchNPU version: 2.7.1.post4\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:24
msgid "注：更多配套关系请参考安装指南的[产品版本配套说明表](./installation_guide.md#环境准备)。"
msgstr "Note: For more compatibility information, please refer to the [Product Version Compatibility Table](./installation_guide.md#environment-preparation) in the installation guide."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:26
msgid "## 快速安装"
msgstr "## Quick Installation"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:28
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"pip install triton-ascend==3.2.1 --extra-index-url=https://triton-ascend.osinfra.cn/pypi/simple\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:30
msgid "## 快速开始"
msgstr "## Quick Start"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:32
msgid "**运行tutorials中向量加法实例验证结果**"
msgstr "**Run the vector addition example in tutorials to verify the result**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:34
msgid ""
"向量加法实例：[01-vector-add.py](../../third_party/ascend/tutorials/01-vector-add.py)\n"
"通过对比Triton算子与PyTorch原生计算的输出结果，证明昇腾NPU设备可正确调用Triton算子并保证计算精度。\n"
msgstr ""
"Vector addition example: [01-vector-add.py](../../third_party/ascend/tutorials/01-vector-add.py)\n"
"By comparing the output results of the Triton operator with PyTorch native computation, it is demonstrated that the Ascend NPU device can correctly invoke the Triton operator and ensure computational accuracy.\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:36
msgid ""
"```bash\n"
"# 设置CANN环境变量（以root用户默认安装路径`/usr/local/Ascend`为例）\n"
"source /usr/local/Ascend/ascend-toolkit/set_env.sh\n"
"# 拉取triton-ascend源码仓及用例\n"
"git clone https://github.com/triton-lang/triton-ascend.git\n"
"# 运行tutorials实例\n"
"python3 ./triton-ascend/third_party/ascend/tutorials/01-vector-add.py\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:38
msgid "观察到类似的输出即说明环境配置正确。"
msgstr "Observing similar output indicates that the environment configuration is correct."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:40
msgid ""
"```shell\n"
"tensor([0.8329, 1.0024, 1.3639,  ..., 1.0796, 1.0406, 1.5811], device='npu:0')\n"
"tensor([0.8329, 1.0024, 1.3639,  ..., 1.0796, 1.0406, 1.5811], device='npu:0')\n"
"The maximum difference between torch and triton is 0.0\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: blank
#: docs/zh/quick_start.md:41
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
